  "remarks": "GBi.010 Designation: a) Lieutenant-colonel b) Commander of the Paratroops Regiment. Other information: Nhate was listed on 18 Jul. 2012 pursuant to paragraph 4 of resolution 2048 (2012) as “Member of the \"Military Command\" which has assumed responsibility for the coup d'état of 12 April 2012. A loyal ally of António Injai, Lt.Col. Júlio Nhate has the material responsibility for the 12 April 2012 coup, having conducted the military operation.”; Listing: Listed by 2048 Committee on 18 Jul 2012",
